{
  "stem": "18397.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Paid a lot of money to get in, in this, with an-- with an exit to the sewers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they figure if they catch the bunker, somebody is going to do this here, they'll go out to the sewers and go out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or well, what can you do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were older people, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They couldn't take it, what they have to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, once I was going with-- with the-- with the group, you know, to-- to make something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the guy came from Vilna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw right away he is a Jewish guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I say, was they in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, which one of them?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I say, over there and on this [INAUDIBLE], you know, this and-- it's a bunker.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You hear about it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're breaking, he says.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're breaking the bunker to get in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They cannot go in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made it the right way, you know, like a-- with a-- so I say, let's go back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this guy was with me, the guy he was, I told you, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the guy who-- who became a commissar, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ring.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was with me because he-- his parents were in the bunker too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a big shot in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We'll continue on the next tape.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
